    <p class="price-note">Honest framing: Breezaire's lower retail price means rebuild-vs-replace math tilts toward replace earlier than for premium brands. We'll always quote both, but often the honest answer is that a new WKL costs less than rebuilding a 12-year-old WKB.</p>
